{
  "text": "The Bayesian fusion structure illustrated in Fig. 7 , is a representation of the newly created trust model given in Fig. 2 ; which is a substitution to the Bayesian network structure given in [CITATION_1] ; where C represents the communication trust, D represents the data trust and T represents the total trust.",
